<section>
<h1>Paste69</h1>

<p>
    Paste69 is a fast and open source pastebin, file bin, and link shortener written in Go.
</p>

<p>
    <a href="https://github.com/watzon/0x45">Star the Project on GitHub ‚≠ê</a>
</p>
</section>

<section>
<div class="info-box">
    <h3>üì¶ CLI Tool Available!</h3>
